summary: 1992 VOLVO 960 SERIES STALLED WHILE DRIVING AT HIGH SPEEDS.  THE POWER WINDOWS AND LOCKS ALSO CEASED FUNCTIONING WHEN THE VEHICLE STALLED.    *KB  THE VEHICLE JERKED PRIOR TO STALLING.  THE VEHICLE BATTERY WOULD GO DEAD IF PARKED ONE DAY.  THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER TWICE BUT THEY WERE UNABLE TO CORRECT THE PROBLEM.  *NM
